in terminal:
$ uv tool install specify-cli --from git+https://github.com/github/spec-kit.git@v0.12.1
$ specify init spec-kit-practice --integration copilot
$ cd spec-kit-practice 
$ specify version   

open a project in VScode, open terminal there (cmd+J)
